		line-height: 60rpx;
		color:#858282;
		/* background: red; */
		border-bottom:1rpx solid #f5f5f5;
		padding-bottom:10rpx;
		}

.outlogin view{width:30%;
		height:60rpx;
		margin:30rpx auto 0rpx; 
